Text: Coal Market Strategies Presentationhave attached the final draft of the CMS presentation Graphics is currently printing up transparencies assembling two bound color copies and burning a CD backup I will bring them up as soon as they are done I am currently working on the narrative for the presentation and should have something ready by Thursday at Stuart

Coal Market Strategieshave attached the latest draft of the coal presentation for the Coal Market Strategies Conference in Scottsdale I am still waiting on an updated version of the bar chart on page from the folks up in EOL I am also forwarding this draft on to Janet Gellici the woman organizing the conference I told her on the phone and in my email that this was only a draft and we will have the final version for her by the end of business on Thursday Let me know of any further changes you would like to make Thanks Stuart
